This is a one time mapping to perform historical update of INSRD_ID in table RCIT_BASE_CLM_APC for AETNA APMCAS and RXC claims for BATCH DATE>=01/01/2013.

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT BCI.CLM_GID , BCI.MBR_GID , BCI.EXTL_SRC_CD ,BCI.DSPN_DT ,BCI.EXTL_LVL1_ID FROM VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV BCI WHERE BCI.INV_ELIG_DT IN ($$INV_ELIG_DT) AND BCI.MODEL_TYP_CD IN ($$MODEL_TYP_CD) AND RTRIM(LTRIM(EXTL_SRC_CD)) in ($$EXTL_SRC_CD)

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: Exp_Derive_MBR_CUMB_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This variable is used to evaluate LKP_V_CLAIM_AETNA to get MBR_CUMB_ID (INSRD_ID) for APMCA external source code.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: var_APMCAS_CLAIM_CUMB_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION:
This output only port holds the CUMB_ID (INSRD_ID). Logic for APMCAS: If var_APMCAS_CLAIM_CUMB_ID is null then evaluate look up LKP_T_MBR_XWALK based on MBR_GID to get CUMB_ID else use var_APMCAS_CLAIM_CUMB_ID value.
FOR RXC: evaluate look up LKP_T_MBR_XWALK based on MBR_GID to get CUMB_ID
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: out_CUMB_ID

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Added to identify Aetna RXC claims.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID_INSRD_ID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT RTRIM(VRAP.TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID.EXTL_SRC_CD) as EXTL_SRC_CD, VRAP.TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID.EXTL_LVL1_ID as EXTL_LVL1_ID, VRAP.TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID.CORP_CD as CORP_CD, VRAP.TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID.EFF_DT as EFF_DT, VRAP.TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID.EXP_DT as EXP_DT FROM VRAP.TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID WHERE RTRIM(VRAP.TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID.EXTL_SRC_CD)='RXC' AND VRAP.TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID.CORP_CD=2

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: EXTL_SRC_CD = in_EXTL_SRC_CD AND EXTL_LVL1_ID = in_EXTL_LVL1_ID AND CORP_CD = in_CORP_CD AND EFF_DT <= in_DSPN_DT AND EXP_DT >= in_DSPN_DT

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF(EXTL_SRC_CD='RXC',IIF(ISNULL(:LKP.LKP_TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID_INSRD_ID(EXTL_SRC_CD,EXTL_LVL1_ID,2,DSPN_DT)),0,1),1)
//For Extl_SRC_CD, lookup TCORP_EXTL_LVL1_ID to identify and process only Aetna RXC claims. For APMCAS, consider all claims to process.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: out_AET_CLAIM

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION:
Added by Pooja on 03/11/2013 for ITPR004713 Invoice Claim Extract project --
This look up is added to return MBR_XWALK_ID as CUMB_ID (APC INSRD_ID) from EDW table DWCORP.T_MBR_XWALK based on MBR_GID.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_T_MBR_XWALK

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT max(T_MBR_XWALK.MBR_XWALK_ID) AS MBR_XWALK_ID, T_MBR_XWALK.MBR_GID as MBR_GID FROM DWCORP.T_MBR_XWALK T_MBR_XWALK WHERE T_MBR_XWALK .rec_stus_cd='A' GROUP BY T_MBR_XWALK.MBR_GID
